      <title>Version 1.122.0</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>ClashX v1.122.0</h2>

<h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Fix auto-update</strong> — Added Sparkle EdDSA signing key (SUPublicEDKey) required by Sparkle 2.x. This fixes the "Check for Updates" menu being greyed out and the "Unable to check for updates" error on startup.</li>
</ul>

<p>Minimum system requirement: macOS 10.14.</p>
