    <item>
      <title>Version 1.121.0</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>ClashX v1.121.0</h2>

<h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Helper installation optimization</strong> — Silent fallback from SMJobBless to legacy installation when SMJobBless fails, no more blessError dialog.</li>
  <li><strong>Dashboard auto-connect</strong> — Built-in Yacd-meta dashboard now passes hostname/port/secret URL params to auto-connect to the Clash API.</li>
  <li><strong>Remove dead link</strong> — Removed obsolete Clash core 1.0.0 upgrade alert (Dreamacro wiki URL is now 404).</li>
  <li><strong>Build fix</strong> — Fixed SwiftLint build phase script quoting for paths containing spaces.</li>
</ul>

<p>Minimum system requirement: macOS 10.14.</p>
      ]]></description>
